<div class="sect2 sect" id="byobu-resources"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title">Risorse</h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents"><div class="list itemizedlist"><ul class="list itemizedlist">
<li class="list itemizedlist">
        <p class="para">Per maggiori informazioni riguardo <span class="app application">screen</span>, consultare il <a href="http://www.gnu.org/software/screen/" class="ulink" title="http://www.gnu.org/software/screen/">sito web di screen</a>.</p>
      </li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">
        <p class="para">E la pagina della <a href="https://help.ubuntu.com/community/Screen" class="ulink" title="https://help.ubuntu.com/community/Screen">documentazione della comunità su screen</a>.</p>
      </li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">
        <p class="para">Per maggiori informazioni, consultare anche la <a href="https://launchpad.net/byobu" class="ulink" title="https://launchpad.net/byobu">project page</a> di <span class="app application">byobu</span>.</p>
      </li>
</ul></div></div></div>
</div></div>
